    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting ways with my trusty daily driver, and it's ready for a new adventure! It\u2019s been well-loved and is in solid shape, running smoothly and looking great. If you're looking for a dependable ride that\u2019s been cared for and is ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you'll really love how it drives!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
