      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This naturally aspirated powerhouse utilizes individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double-VANOS to achieve a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Mechanically sound, the vehicle has received critical preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. The chassis is equipped with functional Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M differential lock, ensuring precise lateral dynamics and corner-exit traction. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with its age, the structural integrity and drivetrain performance remain uncompromised. A mechanically honest example optimized for performance longevity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Reliable engine. Minor interior wear. Clean title. Ready for pickup.",
      "price": 34000.0,
