    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking reliability paired with a premium feel. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss and has been regularly waxed, though it shows a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with standard road use. Inside, the cabin is a clean, smoke-free environment; the leather seats remain soft and supportive, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All technological features, including the navigation, premium sound system, and safety sensors, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no hesitations, backed by a comprehensive service history and a recent oil change. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a solid, honest car that drives as well as it looks, perfect for someone who values a well-cared-for machine.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
